<item>
            <title>[WINK-235] Fix issue with using Locale objects inside ResponseBuilder</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WINK-235</link>
                <project id="12310940" key="WINK">Wink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Using a Locale object will not always produce the correct HTTP response header.  Should explicitly call toString on it in the ResponseBuilder for the Content-Language header to be set.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12441994">WINK-235</key>
            <summary>Fix issue with using Locale objects inside ResponseBuilder</summary>
